data.description: MUST SEE!!!! Charming Bouquet Village Two-Story Home with No Mello-Roos!!! This delightful two-bedroom, one-bathroom home is serenely nestled at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac. Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan that bathes the living room and dining area in natural light. The home features a cozy, wraparound, enclosed private patio, perfect for pets or hosting events. Upstairs, you'll find two bedrooms and one bathroom, complete with a convenient walk-in closet. This property also includes two designated covered carport parking spaces and additional storage cabinets. Take advantage of the wonderful community amenities, including a pool, playground, and basketball court. Furthermore, this home offers the convenience of being within walking distance of acclaimed schools and is just a short stroll away from shopping and a variety of delectable dining options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this peaceful retreat your own.
